that VI has done more for us.  It is simply not true.   Stacking issues were game wide.  Adding more ports and transes isn't what I call doing more for us.  Adding enhancements that truly don't effect the sub-uber game that greatly was more because so many were obtaining level 60 than it was for class balancing.  And that was straight from Alans mouth at the Baltimore Fan Faire.  I'm not going to flame them.  I'm simply disappointed.  Thats all.  Hasn't stopped me from playing... yet.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Yes, the complaints are annoying.  But it is more because of HOW they are presented than WHEN or HOW OFTEN they are presented.<br>
